snippet.title: DeFi Land Trailer - Multichain Farming Metaverse
snippet.description:
Introducing DeFi Land, an agricultural utopia that is more than meets the eye. With eclectic pets to love, beautiful fish to catch, and a universe of DeFi to explore, you are sure to find a home in our digital realm. Our village is governed by our $DFL and $GOLDY tokens that are powered by that Solana blockchain.  Come join our family to Play and Earn by various farming activities. 

Learn more about DeFi Land at https://linktr.ee/defiland
